  "blurb": "A six-bedroom beachfront villa on Nathon's shore pairs an unobstructed sunset view and a beachside infinity pool with resort-standard daily service, sleeping up to twelve across flexible whole-villa or room-based stays.",
  "detail": "Set directly on the sand at Nathon Beach, this six-bedroom villa (four main bedrooms plus two additional) accommodates up to twelve guests, adults and children alike, and can be booked as a full exclusive stay or by individual room. A glass-edged infinity pool runs along the beachfront lawn, framed by palms and an open-air sala, with steps leading straight down to the water and an uninterrupted sunset view across the gulf.\n\nGuest access extends to a fitness room, a media room, a private putting green, an outdoor pool table and lounge deck, and a fully equipped kitchen with barbecue, giving the villa the feel of a small resort run at a private scale. Bedrooms range from canopied four-poster suites with sea-facing terraces to twin bunk rooms suited to children, each with an ensuite bathroom finished in stone and timber.\n\nDaily service is included in the rate: continental breakfast, a breakfast-and-Thai-lunch cooking service, daily pool cleaning, maid standby from 8am to 5pm, an on-call villa manager and concierge, plus complimentary electricity, water and Wi-Fi. Dinner or barbecue cooking can be arranged for an additional THB 2,000 per meal for up to twelve guests; food and provisioning are charged to the guest account, with a market fee of 20% of cost (minimum THB 650, plus 7% VAT).\n\nA security deposit of USD 1,000 (or currency equivalent) is collected at check-in per villa and refunded at check-out.",
